article.headline: Agbo's 19 lead Boise State past Vanguard 89-55
article.description: — Chibuzo Agbo had 19 points in Boise State's 89-55 win against Vanguard on Tuesday night in the season opener for both teams.
article.linkText: Agbo's 19 lead Boise State past Vanguard 89-55
article.story: BOISE, Idaho -- — Chibuzo Agbo had 19 points in Boise State's 89-55 win against Vanguard on Tuesday night in the season opener for both teams. Agbo added seven rebounds for the Broncos. O'Mar Stanley scored 16 points and added seven rebounds. Cam Martin had 12 points, 13 rebounds, four assists and two steals. Nico Dasca led the way for the Lions with nine points. Vanguard also got eight points and three steals from Phillip Willis. Jackson Larsen also had eight points and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
